Welcome to Forum Browser!

Basics:

 * To change or add forums, click the 'Forums' button
 * Use the context menu button to access help for the current view as well as options for that view

Skin Mods:
 It is recommended that you install the skin mods from the Forum Browser settings under the category 'Skin Mods'.
 There are 2 mods:
  * Forum Browser font: Displays better and provides smilies and better looking post quotes.
  * Enhanced Keyboard: Replaces the XBMC keyboard. Has a button that toggles a large typing area for better editing of posts.
 